[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Investigating test coverage**\n\nI’m considering how normal tests could improve coverage by including macros. I might need to provide dependencies to prevent ClassNotFound errors for LoggingAdapter or blackbox.Context. I’ve noticed that Scala reflection is often required at compile time for macro annotations, and I should remember that ccompat annotations were removed in 2.0.0-M1, so it's important to update the tests accordingly. The remaining public API is org.apache.pekko.macros.LogHelper, but it seems to extend LogHelperMacro, which requires LoggingAdapter and scala.reflect macros. I should also look into inspecting the bytecode with javap and checking the source documentation.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0b3376c9a215b0e4016a430dc3ae54819398d323d52a7bf22f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQw3KFzEwlsNNd6sAjy9ggYqnn6s1eqcLdhQP8ti1XtOdpfJnbJ1jwhWPg-SkfPtCALO_xYmaqqZ-UodVC5wIvbqx8-uKe6g3XASWGGUwVgH_c7eCNeQoY97K0bGfTbiegL9lVW7qAsUxUbVPaPMTmguq3jkuwTKh-2DXCklSVtVEmhvQJuc1AA8ftmwcXwBpW8tjmua_4eDrJjQIdsOxIP9_MRggDcuqkj7eTvRH4_FpKy4Wj3XPAq8R9SlnzpxbYquCbW-NZ5G9DgHdjqv7zH6MKgOg8ivPVm-77I6PHvBv2UfSgRZfqUYx9iiuDNxpfhxmVmCB-2FEbn5x4MWhFdWW7VCQfngDx1_El751oQYRQi7PxX4GRgv8gekEs3bWMMTsjL-yj8axrCk45JwJXfg2I-3EAFMA-u_RS2HptwFxgGfyQdze9BjuYVmgskTkt-h1U8D1E61uZGGZU3lhzGfnmw_sfQONmcRE_dpQ01Av_pK8dTrUh7eb_BvnZtTwda-s9ahJZCcztQ2W6VKisMjPEfkGRs3Xk8uBq-_imW0pEVAOR9ioEw1ihyqLpyN3CKX08bjMNWDXQcFhRFUIVuweoLReqzy1SwW5OxHkATIia0-GS2yX0Q-v3pSNgysLq0RTOaLmbSDL-nNOgC3e_KQFLoZ_2LR7jytt3E1oOzbLCJ9WG4awkbR6BIv5owKrHY6MymgcKEkbsI1Dv8eAv8x4FNhvvESz6DAj3MFoSvNYOtGrfcwuNnJ1yhX45SZ6-y7WJbUNL2dkJ5uxSG5S3koGCa2X_0BpmG69Q4pdN0-C-W5V56w98nhHDCIcRhK1hsQj4PNBgBvGCgbxO2nL9cTvds9U7ukioFdKl3lzNb1uCd4fpkSRwXdIigK7plfKkercc6FM2s_OqzmcLO2sv-Ge7vHG2PTF9cl3p1rVY7hlPNe8qopWuZis1i2Ey5yINnzquo10kqx32nV3DcUTxKsUbuJnLizvzMomunERQrGcMVJF7-njtSdAlazRnZ_Og2DCS2Kks1AcpE3c